replies.msg:
師兄有少少講錯咗<br />
C入面嘅<br />
將pointer當argument傳入function<br />
唔係pass by reference嚟<br />
而係pass by value(of reference)<br />
C入面另外有一種pass by reference嘅語法<br />
<span class="gold">(pointer version) (i.e. pass by value (of reference) )</span><br />
<pre><code data-type="c">void foo(int* bar) {
    bar += 1;
}
int num = 2;
foo(&amp;num);
// num == 3</code></pre><br />
<span class="gold">(reference version) (i.e. pass by reference)</span><br />
<pre><code data-type="c">void foo(int&amp; bar) {
    bar += 1;
}
int num = 2;
foo(num);
// num == 3</code></pre>

